        "type": "paragraph",
        "snippet": "Emotional cutoff counseling in Vancouver, BC, is available through specialists in Emotion-Focused Therapy (EFT), trauma-informed care, and attachment-based therapies. Leading providers include Wellspring Counselling, Emotion Wise Counselling, and Lotus Therapy & Counselling Centre, which help address family estrangement, relationship avoidance, and deep-seated emotional disengagement. wellspringcounselling.ca +2",
