          },
          {
            "snippet": "Trauma-Informed Care: Lotus Therapy & Counselling Centre uses holistic approaches, integrating body and mind to address the root causes of emotional distance."
          },
          {
            "snippet": "Reduced-Cost Options: Moving Forward Family Services provides affordable, long-term counseling, while Willow Tree Counselling lists clinics with interns.",
